javavis.jip2d.base
Class JIPFunctionLoader

java.lang.Object
  javavis.jip2d.base.JIPFunctionLoader

public class JIPFunctionLoader
extends java.lang.Object

This class receives a descriptor file of functions and it loads an array with this functions. The file must have this syntax: FNombreFuncion1 {
parameter11=value11;
parameter21=value21;
}

FNombreFuncion2 {
parameter12=value12;
parameter22=value22;
}

...
The value of the parameters depends on type:
BOOL : true o false
IMAGE : string with the JIP image name
STRING : string
INT : numerical
FLOAT : numerical

Use:
JIPFunctionLoader loader = new JIPFunctionLoader("functions_file_descriptor");

JIPFunction [] funcions = loader.getFunctions();
